#include <iostream>
#include <math.h>
using namespace std;
 
bool isPerfectSquare(long long int x)
{
    int s = sqrt(x);
    return (s*s == x);
}
 
bool isFibonacci(long long int y)
{
    return isPerfectSquare(5*y*y + 4) ||
           isPerfectSquare(5*y*y - 4);
}
 
int main()
{
	long long int n;
  int t;
  cin>>t;
  while(t>0)
  {
  	cin>>n;
  	
     isFibonacci(n)? cout <<"is fibo\n":
                     cout <<"not fibo\n" ;
  t--;
  }
  return 0;
}
